event AssetAdded(address indexed collateralAsset, bytes4 pluginSelector)
event OwnershipTransferred(address indexed previousOwner, address indexed newOwner)
event PluginAdded(address indexed plugin, bytes4 pluginSelector)
function addCollateral(address market, address collateralAsset, tuple(address flp, bytes4 loanSelector, bytes4 swapSelector) asset, uint256 leverage)
function addMarket(address market, tuple(address flp, bytes4 loanSelector, bytes4 swapSelector) asset)
function assets(address) view returns (address flp, bytes4 loanSelector, bytes4 swapSelector)
function executeMultiplier(address market, address collateralAsset, uint256 initialAmount, uint256 leverage, bytes swapData, uint256 minAmountOut)
function plugins(bytes4) view returns (address endpoint, bytes config)
function withdrawMultiplier(address market, address collateralAsset, uint256 sellAmount, bytes swapData, uint256 minBaseOut)
